room_title: Escape room "Detention" by Escape Marquette in Marquette
room_address: 130 W Washington St Suite L-4 Marquette, MI 49855
room_description: Oh man! You've really done it this time, DETENTION for 60 minutes! Your team must work together in order to solve clues, riddles and puzzles. Only the janitor has the key to escape and you must find him, otherwise you're trapped forever. Time is ticking, will you ESCAPE?
